{"tid":2477863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【連登 商業電台 光明頂 討論區（四十）】","createTime":"2021-04-06T15:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T02:26:53.000Z","uid":35221,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"7c265b4fdadaa0bbb21c1b9a5fee79d35372adb0","tid":2477863,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T15:20:38.000Z","msg":"指點江山，笑傲江湖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會當凌絕頂，一覽眾山小 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n午夜會高峰，煮酒論英雄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多少天下事，盡付笑談中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人傑地靈，光明頂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n登絕嶺，看世界，群雄聽晚繼續決戰光明頂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雷霆881商業一台<br />\n星期一至五 2300-0000<br />\n陶傑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、鮑偉聰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光明頂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d165739ed3fc8d9a0204c4ac15bd4c79eafea5","tid":2477863,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T15:20:43.000Z","msg":"第一帖 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/9220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/9220</a><br />\n第二帖 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/137184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/137184</a><br />\n第三帖 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/211443\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/211443</a><br />\n第四帖 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/399170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/399170</a><br />\n第五帖 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/544564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/544564</a><br />\n第六帖 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/648754\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla