6b9ad8465eb0c129652d5ee1e8e914b0ec4","tid":2477863,"uid":39133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:01:39.000Z","msg":"所以我成日都唔番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:02:42.000Z","msg":"鮑sir 啲道行未夠深<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33469e7a00cf321c3a08be6a6145e6485317e33","tid":2477863,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:02:45.000Z","msg":"報新聞呢條友d口音好難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9093419fd129d9fea534a68b2de22c705e31754","tid":2477863,"uid":23993,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:03:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/839853345/posts/10158884417013346/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F839853345%2Fposts%2F10158884417013346%2F&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=a7abfbc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/839853345/posts/10158884417013346/</a><br />\n<br />\n「彈出彈入的劉細良」<br />\n<br />\n過往劉細良對本土派甚至獨派，極盡嘲諷踐踏之能事，族繁不及備載，在此不再贅述。<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月7日，劉細良與陶君行在《奪命Loudzone》質疑「光復香港，時代革命」應否作為反送中運動的代表口號，並將之連結到「港獨劇本」，明言必須「主權無涉」，撕走「港獨」標籤。<br />\n<br />\n2019年12月8日，劉細良終於想通如何將「光復香港，時代革命」去港獨化、去脈絡化甚至去政治化，認定參與抗爭的青年與2014-16本土派掀起政治巨變無關，變成虛無的精神符號，好讓「城寨之友」安心使用。<br />\n<br />\n於是無論在《城寨》節目，人前人後，都盡情消費這句口號，甚至大剌剌地放在案頭及背後，用作自我宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n然而因為7月1日《國安法》正式生效，開始偷偷收起被官方指定違法、侵害主權的「光復香港，時代革命」標語，自2020年7月23日，徹底在《城寨》所有節目內消失。反正這不過是「拿來主義」的消費品，從來不是他本人及其聽眾的核心信念，用完自然可棄。<br />\n<br />\n鬧其契弟，未免太睇小佢，劉細良根本屬典型人渣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZhoFrG2DRYtnMp1LFia8cpgotXY86kqC9oBNHL714kFs?filename=sLG7cOn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsLG7cOn.png&h=222ac3c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbhWwLzuCzpfJ3tuFe6cL5TqHDwht32RZ9PqgF4K3qNAB?filename=bxr3vAb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbxr3vAb.png&h=7cee2f80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e11194c9b0a84d562543ef1318113da69b108717","tid":2477863,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:03:10.000Z","msg":"司徒華件事係點"},{"pid":"f1347a40460d740ad7b32d449cbce86472d53ba1","tid":2477863,"uid":28202,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"12bdf99c69751d3637637d9331b6fdd4c362139c","tid":2477863,"uid":29787,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T15:57:21.000Z","msg":"一句到尾，根本就唔應該捉鬼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"鮑生佢最後終於點題<br />\n就係細良同民主黨捉咗好多年鬼,<br />\n根本係手段嚟,唔係多疑咁簡單<br />\n係攞嚟排除威脅到自己利益既人<br />\n而且仲長時間都係咁做"},{"pid":"3c3d4c331ca22901a680f741bef4ae29a7765d96","tid":2477863,"uid":272696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b33469e7a00cf321c3a08be6a6145e6485317e33","tid":2477863,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:02:45.000Z","msg":"報新聞呢條友d口音好難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:04:04.000Z","msg":"好L似777啲口音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a63dc314583e09d873ea35cea547d70758bc74","tid":2477863,"uid":14718,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"522822cdebfe45d1f1b96bd276c20f1f16be456c","tid":2477863,"uid":48139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34f418913a72bb3bc7e26fe7a04c5ab518fcdba3","tid":2477863,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"363f4655438b49eac6bf5922bf41d84b7208bf48","tid":2477863,"uid":28202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"咪係陶生你自己炒起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"